commits.message:
Add rate limiting to sync routes

Adds rate limiting to the staff/sync, students/sync and school/sync
routes. Sets the throttle limit to 3 requests every minute. This will
help prevent any constant requests to the server to fetch data and help
prevent clogging up the queue worker if the sync button is pressed too
many times.

Implement AssemblyServiceProvider, bind MISInterface

Implements a new AssemblyServiceProvider which binds an MISInterface to
the service container. Returns a new instance of Assembly service class
with the client ID and client secret.

Updates the Assembly class to accept the client ID and secret through
the constructor and use these keys in the class.

Updates any implementation of the Assembly class throughout the code
base, i.e. in the jobs to use the MISInterface instead. This will allow
for switching out the Assembly class for another implementation if
required further down the line.

Eager load groups and tags to fix n+1

Eager loads the groups and tags on the concerns.index view to prevent
n+1 SQL query problem.

Use spatie media library for attachments

Uses spatie/media-library package to save media to attachments
collection for concerns. Needs to be able to save the attachments and
body map when initially creating the concern as well.

Save concern media on creation using spatie/media-library

Updates the ConcernController to call a saveMedia() method and passes
the requested file attachments and the bodymap. The saveMedia method
uses spatie/media-library package and saves the attachments to an
attachments collection. Also converts the base64 bodymap image and saves
to an attachments collection and returns a 200 response.

Remove Image class and ImageInterface class

Removes the Image class and the ImageInterface class. Both are now
redundant with the use of spatie/media-library package to convert the
base64 image.

Improve UI for concerns.show

Improves the UI for the concerns.show view splitting it into tabs; one
for main concern details, one for concern attachments and one to list
the students involved in the concern.
Add edit and delete buttons to concerns.show UI
Change wording from logged to reported

Allow multiple file upload on attachments.create

Allows multiple file uploads on the attachments.create view. Updates the
input box styles so more consistent without the box shadows.
Update data protection modal text

Improve UI for students profile page

Improve the UI for the students profile page so items are under tabs and
tidier.

Fix for clearing body map, minor UI updates

Fixes the body map so when it is cleared and closed, the input is
cleared so no blank body maps are sent to the request.
